The `WithOpenWebUI()` returns an instance of `IResourceBuilder<OllamaResource>` so any chanid extension method will configure the `OllamaResource` not `OpenWebUIResource`.

Instead, you should use the `configureContainer` parameter of `WithOpenWebUI`:

```csharp
var ollama = builder.AddOllama("ollama")
    .WithDataVolume()
    .WithOpenWebUI(c =>
    {
        //configure open web ui here
        c.WithEnvironment("DCP_IDE_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_SECONDS", "600");
    });
```
